name: Community Graffiti Box 1
description: This box contains a single community-designed graffiti pattern. A portion of the proceeds is shared equally among the included creators.

name: Collectible Pins Capsule Series 1
description: This capsule contains a single Series 1 collectible pin. Collectible pins can be displayed on your profile.

name: Cologne 2016 Legends (Holo/Foil)
description:
This capsule contains a single Cologne 2016 participant Holo or Foil sticker.

50% of the proceeds from the sale of this capsule support the included players and organizations.

That sticker can be applied to any weapon you own and can be scraped to look more worn. You can scrape the same sticker multiple times, making it a bit more worn each time, until it is removed from the weapon.
